<section class="section" style="padding-top:48px;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">About Us</span>
      <h2>A dedicated team focused on one thing: approvable petitions</h2>
      <p>Immigration Horizons was built around a simple idea — every petition should be written to the same standard USCIS holds it to. We work with individuals, and with attorneys and paralegals who need extra hands on a case.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-strip">
      <div class="stat"><strong><%= stats.casesHandled %></strong><span>Cases Handled</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><strong><%= stats.yearsExperience %></strong><span>Years Experience</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><strong>Global</strong><span>Clients Across Continents</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><strong>Multi-lingual</strong><span>Support Available</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-40">
      <p>We follow the same 8-point standard on every case — from personalized strategy to a dedicated point of contact. <a href="/#why-us">See all the reasons clients choose us →</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="section-head mt-40">
      <span class="eyebrow">Our Team</span>
      <h2>Meet the team</h2>
    </div>
    <%- include('partials/team') %>

    <div class="cta-band mt-40">
      <h2>Let's talk about your case</h2>
      <p>Tell us about your background and what you're trying to achieve — we'll follow up with next steps.</p>
      <a href="/consultation" class="btn btn-blue">Book Your Free Consultation</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
